ABOUT US

   Founded in 2010, we are the leading online luxury magazine and social
   media hub devoted exclusively to high-end jewellery and watches. Based
   in London, we have a monthly global reach of over 2.8 million across
   our platforms. With experts and contributors around the globe, we bring
   you the latest and the best news, reviews and videos from this exciting
   and glamorous world.
